title: Where to travel as the Australian dollar falls
text:
Where to travel as the Australian dol... Where to travel as the Australian dollar falls 3 hrs ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
Forget London, New York or Bali. If you are looking to get more bang for your travel buck now that the Australian dollar has fallen, you should consider a trip to New Zealand, Brazil, Colombia, Russia or Norway.   Sydney Morning Herald.
